Clear overcast nice day.

column2: spotted two very large snapping turtles in lake.

column1: Spotted two black bear on shoreline.

column2: Lake is clear to 14 feet. Sunny day. Nice....Always have one Loon on lake. This year we have two. Babies...?????
lake about a 12-14 inchs higher then normal

column1: Lots of baby bullheads in lake.  Many schools swimming around.. have not noticed before- but- did not try to find either. Spring lake was very clear. about 14-15 feet now about 5 feet..(Cloudy)

column2: Lots of BULLHEAD schools number in the thousands...several schools..Is this good or bad....???

column1: two otters in lake...

column2: lots of bullhead.  fishing has been poor. The past 4 weeks. not sure how the Trout did over last winter.

column1: Lake water is high Water seems clear with some alge in the water...

column2: been fishing a lot on Crescent but- have not be getting any Trout Seems like a lot might have died over last winter.???. Their are a lot of Bullhead in the lake many schools of small bullhead.
nice sunny day. lake water is not clear like drinking water. but- it appear green when looking at the whole lake.

column1: if you take a bucket of water out it will look clear.  John Dow.

column2: Lake is very clear. Not sure what to call lake color as it is clear but- from a distance looks green.
lots of pollen dusting on the lake.

column1: cows in the lake.

column2: This year 2016  lake is very clear. With some alge  present. And clarity is at 9 to 10 feet.  Water clarity slowly goes down as you move disk..     ... Is there a reason for the clearer lake water on Crescent.     The bottom is very grassy....   With a lot more lily pads. in the lake....
notice over by boat landing a lot of green slimy moss. very stringy like thread.. its below and above the water...
water is clear to 3.6 feet. water does not look green but- dirty.???
1. Lake is clean to 12 to 13 ft. Small amount of green dots in water but- very clear looking.

column1: 2. Very few lilly pads for this time of year. Bass lake about the same.
3. Big black BEAR come to our house last night. Could not scare HIM AWAY. HE EAT ALL BIRD FEEDERS AND
COULD CARE LESS THAT WE WERE MAKING NOISE TRYING TO SCARE HIM AWAY. Held his ground.
4.  Two loons on lake one large and one small. both came at the same time this year. One has a hard time getting
out of the lake.
5.  Great sunny day..

column2: We live on this lake and we had a bear in our bird feeders. We could not chase him away. He was not scared at all of us.
over cast nice warm day. Did not see a lot of fish kill this season.of Sun fish and frogs this year. But there were some Frogs that were dead by our Dock.

lake is very high a little over a foot. best guess. My neighbor and my dock are under water. one family of loons had 2 babies. They are doing fine. I made a floating loon nest with a 4x4 pallet. This is the 2nd year they used it.
8 feet Secchi depth.  We have a loon nest they had two chicks and one is gone.?? The other baby loon is doing just great. Lake is quite high- guess about 1-1/2 feet. higher then last year.
lake clear but looks green suspect because of the GREEN GRASSY bottom of the lake. My opinion is the Satillite shows it greener then it is.??? Depth of secchi is 8.5 feet

column1: 2.Not sure on fish kill this year. looks minor.
3. Lots of visible mud/painted turtles
4. Two loons are back again this year.They had babies last year.
5. We put out the Loon lodge again this year. Its a pallet 4x4 ft.
6. Bright sunny day.

column2: partly sunny. lake was windy. Loons are here they layed one egg about 4days ago.?. large green with dots..not sure if loon is sitting one this egg.?? I don't think lake is green. seems clear but dark.?
lake looks good. loon is sitting on nest.

column1: question. the lake appears to look good for the 10 feet that I see. does not look green or brown. when looking straight down. however- when looking for land it looks green.??? what should I call it.?

4. lake to me looks green from the road. might be do to all the trees. but- lake currently does not look green from boat.??  not understanding what to call the appearance of lake. to me its not as green as it appears from road.???

column2: lake is a little green.? we had a lot of rain. Lake is very high.
